I"¯<p>When trying to copy long paragraphs of text from my phone to my computer, I noticed that there is no easy way to just do that. <a href="https://clippo.mateffy.me">Clippo</a> tries to solve that problem.</p>

<p><br /></p>

<p><a href="https://clippo.mateffy.me">Clippo</a> is a small web service through which you can securely share your clipboard with many devices. Using a small authentication code, you can connect two devices and then exchange text or images by simply pasting it onto the site.</p>

<h2 id="features">Features</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Securely connect two devices by scanning a QR code or by entering a 6-character code</li>
  <li>Send text, images and videos</li>
</ul>
